Movie search module 
Version 1.0 11/18/2015

General Usage Note:

Things you need:

Internet connection.
Windows/Mac computer with any poplular web browser.
Node and Express server
Please follow simple steps to execute the application.

1.In order to successfully run the application you need to unzip the file .

Open the Shell/command line and browse inside the unzipped directory/folder, once inside type is command:> node app.js to start express the web server. 

Then open your web browser and type --> Localhost:8000 and press enter. 

If all goes well, web browser will automatically load the application. 

